{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"The Taming Tool","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

Plant those "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"Cucumber Seeds"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" on farmland. Once grown, harvest the "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"Cucumbers"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":".

Now, the crucial step: craft the cucumber into "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"Sliced Cucumber"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":". This is what the little fuzzballs actually want."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Regional Rodents","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

Word on the block is, hamsters adapt. Expect different fur stylings depending on where they originated. Some coats are more... "},{"color":"gold","italic":true,"text":"exclusive"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" than others.
Breeding can sometimes result in new white markings."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Taming Revisited","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

Right, the actual taming.
Remember: "},{"color":"dark_purple","text":"Sneak"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":". Hold "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"Sliced Cucumber"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":". Approach slowly. Hope it doesn't notice your desperation. Repeat until furry friend acquired."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Basic Care","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

They follow. Constantly.
Right-click your tamed hamster to make it "},{"color":"dark_purple","text":"Sit/Stay"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":". It might fall asleep. Right-click again to resume the stalking."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Feeding: Healing","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

If your hamster has had a disagreement with, well, anything, feed it "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"seeds or basic crops"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" to patch it up.

For serious healing, craft "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"Hamster Food Mix"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" (sunflower seeds, pumpkin seeds, carrot, wheat seeds)."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Feeding: Pickiness","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

Do not feed it the same mundane item twice in a row. It has standards. It will refuse.

Exceptions: "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"Hamster Food Mix"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" (gourmet stuff) and "},{"color":"gold","text":"Steamed Green Beans"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Feeding: Buffs","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

Those "},{"color":"gold","text":"Steamed Green Beans"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"? (Smelt regular Green Beans). They grant Speed, Strength, Absorption & Regen for a bit. Impressive!

...But there is a cooldown before it works again. Less impressive."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Cheek Pouches","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

Inventory... in their face. Feed epic snack to earn trust... and cheek access. Then "},{"color":"dark_purple","text":"Sneak + Right-click"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" a tamed hamster for 6 slots of prime real estate.
If hurt, it can automatically eat "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"Hamster Food Mix"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" from its cheeks if available."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Shoulder Perks","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

Your shoulder companion may alert you to nearby "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"Creepers"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" that have noticed you, or shiny "},{"color":"aqua","text":"Diamonds"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":". Listen for the unique squeaks and sniffs amongst your own panicked breathing.

More on that → → →"}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Creeper Paranoia","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

That panicked squeak? A "},{"color":"dark_green","text":"Creeper"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" has targeted YOU. Not just nearby, "},{"color":"dark_red","italic":true,"text":"*targeting*"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":".

Maybe your hamster is worried its comfy shoulder perch is about to vanish."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Subterranean Shinies","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

Those excited sniffs? Your pocket prospector smells "},{"bold":true,"color":"aqua","text":"Diamonds!"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" Checks a 10-block radius by default.

It pauses between alerts, so listen carefully before you start digging... again."}],"text":""}

{"extra":[{"bold":true,"color":"dark_aqua","text":"Tiny Prospector?","underlined":true},{"color":"dark_gray","text":"

Heard those "},{"color":"aqua","text":"diamond detecting sniffs"},{"color":"dark_gray","text":" from your shoulder? Try letting your fuzzy friend down while it's still got the scent.

If it was really onto something, it might just decide to lead you to the jackpot."}],"text":""}
